      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Affordable, Functional, and Ready to Work! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it gets the job done reliably and has been kept running, though it does show its age with some noticeable wear, minor cosmetic imperfections, and the occasional quirk you'd expect from a well-used car. It's not perfect, but it's honest transportation at an honest price! Mechanically functional and a great option for a budget-conscious buyer who needs a dependable daily driver without the premium price tag. Come take a look \u2014 what you see is what you get! \ud83d\udd11",
