      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid & Dependable \u2014 A Well-Maintained Ride Ready for Its Next Adventure! \u2014 Here's a car that delivers real value! This vehicle is in good condition \u2014 it's been properly cared for, runs smoothly, and presents well both inside and out. You'll find it handles daily driving with confidence, and the overall upkeep reflects an owner who took pride in their vehicle. Minor signs of normal wear are present, as expected, but nothing that takes away from its reliability or appeal. If you're looking for a dependable car at a fair price, this one is well worth a closer look!",
