    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in good condition, and prospective buyers will find it to be a dependable and well-cared-for option. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 the paint retains most of its original luster with only minor surface scratches and light swirl marks consistent with normal use; there are no dents or rust to report. The interior is clean and comfortable, with moderate wear on the driver's seat and floor mats that you'd expect from regular daily driving, but no tears, stains, or damage to speak of. All major mechanical systems are functioning properly \u2014 the engine starts reliably, runs smoothly, and shows no warning lights; the transmission shifts cleanly through all gears. Brakes have adequate life remaining, and tires show even wear with good tread depth. This is a solid, honest used car that has been maintained responsibly and is ready for its next owner without requiring immediate repairs.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "terse_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "terse_7",
      "description": "A poor-condition used car with heavy wear, significant cosmetic damage, and mechanical issues that will require attention.",
